{"title":"Ubuntu18.04 主题美化（MaxOS主题）","uid":"1559d2cf4b481d8b25de999a80211dc5","slug":"Ubuntu18-04-主题美化（MaxOS主题）","date":"2019-09-10T01:56:43.000Z","updated":"2023-09-06T07:14:24.883Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Ubuntu18-04-主题美化（MaxOS主题）.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<p>Ubuntu时可以进行主题的美化，可以改为MacOS主题。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装工具\"><a href=\"#安装工具\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装工具\"></a>安装工具</h3><p>要安装主题，首先要安装三个包</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo apt update</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo apt install gnome-tweak-tool</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo apt install gnome-shell-extensions</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo apt install gnome-shell-extension-dashtodock</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"Tweak修改（注意，下面这些已经经过主题美化了）\"><a href=\"#Tweak修改（注意，下面这些已经经过主题美化了）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Tweak修改（注意，下面这些已经经过主题美化了）\"></a>Tweak修改（注意，下面这些已经经过主题美化了）</h3><ol>\n<li>经过安装三个包后，我们可以打开Tweaks</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles15.png\" alt=\"1\"></p>\n<p>像上面修改，我们可以发现本来在右上角的按钮放到了左上角了。</p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>修改鼠标的指针的样式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles16.png\" alt=\"2\"></p>\n<p>如图，我们可以通过修改cursor ,修改鼠标的箭头的样式。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>去掉Shell的无法修改的感叹号</p>\n<p>Extensions -&gt; User themes 打开它</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles17.png\" alt=\"3\"></p>\n<p><strong>重启</strong>，然后可以发现那个感叹号不见了。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将侧边栏放到底部。</p>\n<p>Extensions -&gt; Dash to dock 点击settings图标，像下面的图，然后进一步修改。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles18.png\" alt=\"4\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"安装主题\"><a href=\"#安装主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装主题\"></a>安装主题</h3><h4 id=\"安装GTK主题\"><a href=\"#安装GTK主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装GTK主题\"></a>安装GTK主题</h4><p><a href=\"https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1013714/\">McHigh Sierra https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1013714/</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1013741/\">McSierra Compact https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1013741/</a></p>\n<p>在第一个链接中。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles19.png\" alt=\"5\"></p>\n<p>下载这个，到桌面或其他比较便于管理的位置。</p>\n<p>然后再这个位置打开terminal</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">tar xvf Sierra-light.tar.xz</span></span></code></pre></div><p>得到解压后的文件。</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo mv Sierra-light /usr/share/themes</span></span></code></pre></div><p>最后在Tweaks中</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles20.png\" alt=\"6\"></p>\n<p>在applications中修改为Sierra-light，我们可以发现GTK主题改变了。</p>\n<h4 id=\"安装shell主题\"><a href=\"#安装shell主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装shell主题\"></a>安装shell主题</h4><p>其实，shell主题和GTK主题一样，也可以在shell中修改为Sierra-light 也可以。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles21.png\" alt=\"7\"></p>\n<p>也可以安装其他主题，比如Sierra-compact-light主题等等。可以在<strong><a href=\"https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/\">https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/</a></strong> 中寻找。</p>\n<h4 id=\"安装icons主题\"><a href=\"#安装icons主题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装icons主题\"></a>安装icons主题</h4><p>我选的是MacOS11主题，不过由于这个主题比较大，下载费时，所以下面给出了百度云链接：</p>\n<p> 链接：<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1tVP9dghyHvNwq4kMNtyu5g\">百度网盘 请输入提取码</a><br>提取码：f34j</p>\n<p>然后放到某一位置，解压，并把解压后得到的文件夹移动到&#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;icons</p>\n<p>最后打开Tweaks，在Appearance 中打开icon，选MacOS11就行。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles22.png\" alt=\"8\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"安装GDM主题（登陆界面主题）\"><a href=\"#安装GDM主题（登陆界面主题）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装GDM主题（登陆界面主题）\"></a>安装GDM主题（登陆界面主题）</h4><p>百度云链接：<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1f-PPWVILeovdIWmvQjXkVw\">百度网盘 请输入提取码</a> <br>提取码：yetv </p>\n<p>来源：<a href=\"https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/p/1207015/\">High Ubunterra - Gnome-look.org</a></p>\n<p>把下载得到的文件解压，得到文件夹，文件夹的内容：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles23.png\" alt=\"9\"></p>\n<p>备份&#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;gnome-shell&#x2F;theme&#x2F;ubuntu.css</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo cp /usr/share/gnome-shell/theme/ubuntu.css /usr/share/gnome-shell/theme/ubuntu.css.backup</span></span></code></pre></div><p>用上图中的ubuntu.css替换掉系统自带的&#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;gnome-shell&#x2F;theme&#x2F;ubuntu.css</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo cp -i ~/Desktop/liu/setaswallpaper/ubuntu.css /usr/share/gnome-shell/theme/ubuntu.css</span></span></code></pre></div><p>（上面的注意位置别写错）</p>\n<p>把SetAsWallpaper脚本文件复制到~&#x2F;.local&#x2F;share&#x2F;nautilus&#x2F;scripts&#x2F;目录下，然后修改下权限（如果需要）</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo cp ~/Desktop/liu/setaswallpaper/SetAsWallpaper ~/.local/share/nautilus/scripts/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo chmod +x SetAsWallpaper</span></span></code></pre></div><p>然后重启nautilus（下面的命令是关闭）</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">nautilus -q</span></span></code></pre></div><p>执行如下命令，修改下 &#x2F;usr&#x2F;share&#x2F;backgrounds 的权限.</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo chmod 777 /usr/share/backgrounds/</span></span></code></pre></div><p>去~&#x2F;.local&#x2F;share&#x2F;nautilus&#x2F;scripts&#x2F; 目录下执行下SetAsWallpaper脚本。</p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #babed8\">sudo ./SetAsWallpape</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>重启系统</strong>（这个必须的）</p>\n<p>不过此时壁纸应该会没了，可以重新设置，另外，最好先设置自己喜欢的壁纸，这样的话得到的登陆界面的模糊界面可以是基于自己选的壁纸了。</p>\n<p>效果图</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles24.png\" alt=\"10\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"其他主题的一些修改\"><a href=\"#其他主题的一些修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"其他主题的一些修改\"></a>其他主题的一些修改</h3><h4 id=\"桌面壁纸和锁屏界面壁纸修改\"><a href=\"#桌面壁纸和锁屏界面壁纸修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"桌面壁纸和锁屏界面壁纸修改\"></a>桌面壁纸和锁屏界面壁纸修改</h4><p>在桌面右键点击，点Change background。可以修改壁纸，当然，我们也可以从网上下载自己喜欢的壁纸，存到~&#x2F;Pictures就行。</p>\n<h4 id=\"头像的修改\"><a href=\"#头像的修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头像的修改\"></a>头像的修改</h4><p>在Settings中，Details -&gt; Users 点击头像，可以选择自己喜欢的图作为自己的头像。</p>\n<h3 id=\"最终成色\"><a href=\"#最终成色\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"最终成色\"></a>最终成色</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles25.png\" alt=\"11\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://ws4.sinaimg.cn/large/006QU0Psly1g67jolkk33j31gy0nsdm7.jpg\" alt=\"12\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles26.png\" alt=\"13\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles27.png\" alt=\"14\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/PJCK/cdn@1.3/images/ubuntu/Ubuntu_articles28.png\" alt=\"15\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"参考链接：\"><a href=\"#参考链接：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考链接：\"></a>参考链接：</h3><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/feipeng8848/p/8970556.html\">给Ubuntu18.04(18.10)安装mac os主题</a></li>\n<li>[<a href=\"https://www.pling.com/s/Gnome/\">Gnome-look.org</a></li>\n</ul>\n","text":" Ubuntu时可以进行主题的美化，可以改为MacOS主题。 安装工具要安装主题，首先要安装三个包 txtsudo apt update sudo apt in...","permalink":"/post/Ubuntu18-04-主题美化（MaxOS主题）","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"},{"name":"Ubuntu","slug":"Ubuntu","count":3,"path":"api/tags/Ubuntu.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装工具</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Tweak%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%EF%BC%88%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E9%9D%A2%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E4%B8%BB%